Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.09,0:00:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR]\NWealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.01,0:00:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold Roger, the King\Nof the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.67,0:00:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,attained this and everything\Nelse the world had to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.47,0:00:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And his dying words drove\Ncountless souls to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.97,0:00:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[GOLD ROGER]\NYou want my treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.56,0:00:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.85,0:00:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I left everything I gathered\Ntogether in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.19,0:00:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you just have to find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.27,0:00:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR] These words lured men\Nto the Grand Line in pursuit of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.57,0:00:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,dreams greater than they've\Never dared to imagine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.07,0:00:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the time known\Nas the Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.32,0:00:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.91,0:00:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.67,0:00:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One Piece!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.92,0:01:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Compass left behind{\i0}\N{\i1}It'll only slow us down{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.39,0:01:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your heart will be your guide{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.64,0:01:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Raise the sails{\i0}\N{\i1}and take the helm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.02,0:01:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That legendary place that the{\i0}\N{\i1}end of the map reveals{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.65,0:01:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is only legendary{\i0}\N{\i1}until someone proves it real{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.41,0:01:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through it all, through all{\i0}\N{\i1}the troubled times, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.41,0:01:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}through the heartache,{\i0}\N{\i1}and through the pain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.12,0:01:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Know that I will be there{\i0}\N{\i1}to stand by you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.38,0:01:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like I know{\i0}\N{\i1}you'll stand by me! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.88,0:01:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.55,0:01:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.43,0:01:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's always room for you{\i0}\N{\i1}if you want to be my friend{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.40,0:02:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are, we are on the cruise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.94,0:02:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.46,0:02:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\N"Hawk-Eye Mihawk!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.84,0:02:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The Great Swordsman\NZoro Falls At Sea!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.26,0:02:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY, YOSAKU gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.81,0:02:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.52,0:02:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.56,0:02:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?! Nami sailed off\Nwith the Going Merry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.60,0:02:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a straight answer!\NNow, what happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.19,0:02:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... It all happened\Nin only a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.16,0:02:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[YOSAKU]\NHey, what's the matter, Big Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.37,0:02:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, I don't really\Nmean to pry or anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.16,0:02:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,but whatcha looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.29,0:02:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well, it's nothing really.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.04,0:03:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice! Now that's a\Nbig bounty pirate...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.38,0:03:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta say, I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.63,0:03:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But Big Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.59,0:03:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're aiming a little\Ntoo high going after Arlong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.30,0:03:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not kidding, that\Nguy's really bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.84,0:03:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He was playing it cool and\Nlaying low for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.22,0:03:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, staying out of sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.51,0:03:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[YOSAKU]\NBut these days,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.26,0:03:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,that maniac is causing\Nall sorts of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.06,0:03:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kinda tough walking away
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,from a 20 million\Nberry bounty though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY] That guy is so\Npowerful that there is the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,slightest, tiniest chance that\Nwe could lose and, well, die...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY, YOSAKU]\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.24,0:03:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[YOSAKU]\NBig Sis Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.03,0:03:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, would you guys\Nmind turning around
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.95,0:03:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,while I change into\Nsomething more comfortable?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.08,0:03:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure... I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.70,0:03:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Changing? Like right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.79,0:03:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.25,0:03:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[YOSAKU, JOHNNY gasp]\NYeah, you're hot-- Uh, it's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.80,0:03:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever met a\Nwoman who's that daring?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.76,0:03:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what do you\Nsay we turn around
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.30,0:03:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and see if she's done yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY]\NGood idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.89,0:03:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH gasp, scream]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.44,0:04:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell do you\Nthink you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.74,0:04:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing business, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.53,0:04:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Use your heads, guys. I'm a\Nthief who only targets pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.28,0:04:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and my next score is this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.28,0:04:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I never said anything about\Nbeing a member of this crew,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.83,0:04:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just traveling\Nwith them, nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.37,0:04:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I only spent a short\Ntime with Luffy and the gang,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.92,0:04:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure had a lot of fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.84,0:04:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure to tell\Nthem that I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.42,0:04:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY, YOSAKU]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.51,0:04:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's truly meant to be,\NI'll see them real soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.43,0:04:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.89,0:04:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[YOSAKU, JOHNNY scream]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.89,0:04:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[YOSAKU, JOHNNY gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.85,0:04:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna be in\Nso much trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.94,0:04:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Our only job was to\Nlook after the ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.19,0:04:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're making\Nus fail miserably!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.36,0:04:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.63,0:05:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the story of how\NBig Sis Nami took the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.59,0:05:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.51,0:05:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.43,0:05:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! She just had to\Nmake a bad situation worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The heartless thief!\NKaya gave us that ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.10,0:05:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NWait! I see a ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.35,0:05:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Going Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.31,0:05:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me where your boat is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.73,0:05:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We have it moored\Nto the restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.90,0:05:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro! Usopp!\NDon't just stand there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.82,0:05:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Take their ship and go get Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.69,0:05:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down...\NLet her keep the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.78,0:05:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust me, that woman is way\Nmore trouble than she's worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.03,0:05:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the only person I'll\Naccept as the ship's navigator!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.09,0:05:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, I'll do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.46,0:05:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're one high-maintenance\Ncaptain, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.17,0:05:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Usopp, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.59,0:05:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NUh, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY, YOSAKU] The ship's\Nready for action, Big Bro Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.68,0:06:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.89,0:06:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I should probably\Nstick around here till
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.52,0:06:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I get this thing settled\Nwith the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.35,0:06:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.23,0:06:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, be careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.44,0:06:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The situation here could\Nget really bad really fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.19,0:06:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Got that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.53,0:06:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE A] We were\Nsupposed to be safe now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.78,0:06:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.78,0:06:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE B] The ship has\Nbeen broken to splinters!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.08,0:06:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there! It's that man!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.12,0:06:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] He came back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.83,0:06:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE OO gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.96,0:06:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE A]\NDon Krieg!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.38,0:06:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The man who destroyed\Nour fleet is back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.92,0:06:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.96,0:06:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[GROUP gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.47,0:06:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... That's him...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.18,0:06:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,--[heartbeat thumps]\N--[ZORO gulps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.81,0:06:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[thumping continues]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.86,0:06:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That man is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.03,0:06:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NThat son of a bitch...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.15,0:07:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That psycho followed us back\Nhere! He's gonna kill us all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.74,0:07:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.24,0:07:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.41,0:07:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.00,0:07:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] That's the man\NI've been looking for...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.88,0:07:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hawk-Eye Mihawk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.75,0:07:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's Mihawk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... The greatest swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.47,0:07:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's gotta be the guy\Nwho destroyed Krieg's fleet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.94,0:07:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He sunk 50 pirate ships out on\Nthe Grand Line all by himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.06,0:07:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like he came\Nback to finish the job,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.19,0:07:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but is that all he wants?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.82,0:07:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute... He just\Nlooks like any ordinary man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.32,0:07:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't even appear to have
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.45,0:07:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,any kind of special\Nweapons with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.03,0:07:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He carries his\Nweapon on his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.08,0:07:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY]\NThat's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.41,0:07:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARNE] He couldn't have\Ndestroyed a galleon like that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.37,0:07:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,using nothing but a sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.67,0:07:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hawk-Eye Mihawk...\Nis a true master.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.05,0:07:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He is without a doubt the\Ngreatest swordsman in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.47,0:08:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO gulps] I never thought\Nthat I would meet him so soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.14,0:08:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The time has come...\Nfor me to fulfill my promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.10,0:08:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE SS]\NYou... You monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.02,0:08:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you doing this to us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.44,0:08:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell have we\Never done to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[MIHAWK]\NJust killing time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.32,0:08:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE SS growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.49,0:08:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.08,0:08:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.71,0:08:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! I missed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.29,0:08:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But I aimed straight for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.21,0:08:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He diverted them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.42,0:08:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE SS gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He changed the\Ncourse of the bullets
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.80,0:08:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,using the tip of his sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.34,0:08:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE SS]\NThat can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.64,0:08:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on! Who do you\Nthink you are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.31,0:08:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got three swords!\NIt couldn't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.14,0:08:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never see a sword handled\Nso gently, or with such grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.57,0:09:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no strength in\Nswordplay based on force.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.07,0:09:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] Did you also use that\Nsword to slice up this ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.16,0:09:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[MIHAWK]\NI did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.62,0:09:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.24,0:09:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.70,0:09:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I set sail for only one\Nreason-- to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.17,0:09:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And what is your goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.71,0:09:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,To beat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.96,0:09:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[MIHAWK chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.17,0:09:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How foolish...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.93,0:09:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got spare time,\Nso let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.93,0:09:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! No way!\NIt's him! Roronoa Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.31,0:09:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Zoro of the\NThree-Swords Style!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.18,0:09:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.60,0:09:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? A pirate hunter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.81,0:09:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.40,0:09:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Luffy, we'd\Nbetter hurry! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.24,0:09:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The Going Merry is about\Nto sail right out of sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.12,0:09:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.99,0:09:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.49,0:09:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a weak, pitiful creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.04,0:10:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[MIHAWK] If you are in fact\Na competent swordsman,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.13,0:10:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you should see the\Ndisparity in our abilities,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.34,0:10:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,even before we cross swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.30,0:10:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I must ask you why have\Nyou challenged me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.18,0:10:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be your courage?\NOr is it simply your ignorance?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.31,0:10:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My ambition drives me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.98,0:10:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Also... I made a promise\NI intend to keep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.23,0:10:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The greatest\Nswordsman in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.90,0:10:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,going up against Roronoa Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.78,0:10:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Two masters of swordplay...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.61,0:10:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of a fight is\Nthis gonna turn out to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.49,0:10:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't a person alive\Nwho can defeat Big Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.99,0:10:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He's already the\Nbest in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.21,0:10:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.79,0:10:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Funny... What do you think\Nyou're gonna do with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.96,0:10:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be more than adequate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.46,0:10:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, you wouldn't kill\Na fly with a cannon, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.76,0:10:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You may have quite the\Nreputation on the East Blue,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.76,0:10:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but that doesn't\Nmean much to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.06,0:10:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This sea is by far\Nthe weakest of the four.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.14,0:10:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, I don't carry any\Nblades smaller than this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.98,0:11:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I have had just about\Nenough of your attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.90,0:11:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NNow, you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.11,0:11:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no idea how\Nbig the world really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.16,0:11:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NOni Giri!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.24,0:11:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[metal clangs]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.16,0:11:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO gasps]\NWhat the--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.42,0:11:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.13,0:11:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Big Bro's\NOni Giri was stopped?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.05,0:11:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's crazy! That attack\Nnever fails to stop an enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.97,0:11:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.97,0:11:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] I can't move my swords!\NWhat has he done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.89,0:11:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No one's been able to defend\Nagainst that technique...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.56,0:11:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He stopped it with\Na pocketknife!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.90,0:11:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No... Th-This\Ncan't be happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.23,0:11:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't be this much\Nbetter than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.82,0:11:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way our skills\Nare this far apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.99,0:11:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO yells] I'm not that far\Nbehind the world's strongest!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.95,0:11:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.29,0:12:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[YOSAKU, JOHNNY whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.25,0:12:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.54,0:12:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.79,0:12:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[YOSAKU, JOHNNY gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just toying with him,\Nright?! Fight for real, Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.42,0:12:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.05,0:12:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be that\Nmuch better than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.68,0:12:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.57,0:12:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Such ferocious swordplay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.50,0:12:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.46,0:12:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE SS]\NHow can he defend against
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.76,0:12:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro's Three-Sword Style\Nwith such a small knife?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.26,0:12:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE VV] He's more\Nof monster with a blade
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.09,0:12:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,than even the great Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.52,0:13:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] I did not devote my\Nentire life to swordsmanship...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.85,0:13:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,to be dispatched\Nby a toy like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.40,0:13:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,--[KUINA] Zoro...\N--[ZORO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.86,0:13:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.57,0:13:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.49,0:13:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.54,0:13:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[KUINA grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.70,0:13:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lucky, Zoro...\Nbeing born as a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.12,0:13:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All I ever wanted was to be\Nthe world's greatest swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.80,0:13:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If only... If I'd\Njust been born a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.38,0:13:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.97,0:13:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NDon't fly off at the mouth,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.30,0:13:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,whining like that\Nafter you beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.35,0:13:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.68,0:13:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're my goal! Do you know\Nhow this makes me feel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.35,0:13:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[KUINA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.43,0:13:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[KUINA]\NZoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.68,0:13:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now promise me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.65,0:13:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise me that someday,\None of us will be
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.73,0:13:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the world's greatest swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.19,0:13:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see who gets there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.78,0:13:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH]\NIt's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.20,0:14:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NTo become the world's strongest!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.95,0:14:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.33,0:14:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.09,0:14:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] I ask that you\Nlet me have that sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.38,0:14:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna get stronger\Nthan she ever was!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.47,0:14:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Strong enough that my name\Nreaches up to the heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.64,0:14:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I am going to be the\Nworld's greatest swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.52,0:14:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised her... I promised...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.23,0:14:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunting, panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.07,0:14:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] I will defeat\Nthis man... for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.28,0:14:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.83,0:14:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO pants]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.08,0:14:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.54,0:14:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.92,0:14:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What weight do you carry\Nupon your shoulders?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.59,0:14:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak up, weakling!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.42,0:14:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you call\Nhim "weakling"!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.26,0:14:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll pay for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.63,0:14:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll teach you a lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.14,0:15:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[YOSAKU, JOHNNY yell]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.05,0:15:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.76,0:15:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yosaku! Johnny! Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.47,0:15:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,--Just stay put!\N--[YOSAKU, JOHNNY growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.23,0:15:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.69,0:15:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunts]\NNo... I won't lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.90,0:15:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse to be defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.65,0:15:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[heartbeat thumps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.08,0:15:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Tiger...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.96,0:15:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NWorld's greatest swordsman...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.79,0:15:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds pretty good!\NThe King of the Pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.92,0:15:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't have any less\Nthan the best on his crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.26,0:15:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\N...Trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You are defeated, yet\Nyou won't step back...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.57,0:16:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.82,0:16:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NI don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.04,0:16:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I will not run...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.91,0:16:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I retreat\Na single step...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.25,0:16:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I would be shattering\Nthe promises I've made.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.04,0:16:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't run...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.63,0:16:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I would lose my honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.51,0:16:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, without that,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.97,0:16:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,there would be nothing\Nleft for me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.51,0:16:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what defeat is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.68,0:16:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO chuckles]\NThen I won't accept defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.81,0:16:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.14,0:16:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather die than give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.27,0:16:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[MIHAWK]\NA strong heart indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.57,0:16:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He chooses death before defeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.07,0:16:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.07,0:16:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir... State your name!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.49,0:16:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I am... Roronoa Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.25,0:16:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[MIHAWK]\NI'll remember it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.54,0:16:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No one as strong as you has\Ncome around in quite some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.55,0:16:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So as a swordsman's courtesy,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.38,0:17:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll use the world's strongest\Nblack sword to finish you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.30,0:17:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you... I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.68,0:17:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE A]\NLook! He took it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.18,0:17:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE B] That's the sword\Nthat sliced up the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.18,0:17:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NSo this is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.81,0:17:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Will it be the\Nworld's strongest...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.90,0:17:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...or death?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.03,0:17:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.94,0:17:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough, Big Bro!\NStop it! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.40,0:17:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] Three-Sword\NStyle Secret Technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.03,0:17:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[MIHAWK]\NFall!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.95,0:17:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NThree Thousand Worlds!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.84,0:17:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NI've lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.42,0:17:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] Never in my life\Ndid I imagine I'd lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.47,0:17:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] So this is the power\Nof the greatest in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.31,0:17:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.65,0:18:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Scars on the back are\Na swordsman's shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.65,0:18:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.28,0:18:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.95,0:18:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[MIHAWK] You shouldn't rush\Nthese things, young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.21,0:18:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NZoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.84,0:18:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[YOSAKU, JOHNNY]\NBig Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.09,0:18:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.51,0:18:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NWhy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.68,0:18:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NI devoted my entire life to
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.14,0:18:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,becoming the world's\Ngreatest swordsman...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.26,0:18:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my choice,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.14,0:18:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'm the only one who\Ngets to call me stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.73,0:18:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NHe's insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.06,0:18:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,His opponent was way\Nout of his league!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.61,0:18:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How this fight would end\Nwas clear from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.03,0:18:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why choose death?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.61,0:18:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.20,0:18:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up your ambition and live!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.28,0:18:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the power of the\NGrand Line; it's terrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.96,0:18:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The Pirate Hunter Zoro was as\Nhelpless as a newborn baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.50,0:19:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NDamn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.63,0:19:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[YOSAKU, JOHNNY]\NBig bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.84,0:19:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.55,0:19:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He must be some kind of freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.81,0:19:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.06,0:19:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So that loudmouthed little twerp\Nhas the power of a Devil Fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.52,0:19:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NBastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.56,0:19:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[MIHAWK] Are you that\Nyoung warrior's comrade?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.36,0:19:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed with you\Nfor not interfering.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.74,0:19:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[MIHAWK] There's nothing\Nto be upset about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.33,0:19:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Your friend will live.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.04,0:19:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.04,0:19:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[YOSAKU]\NBig Bro! Say something, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.37,0:19:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NZoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.67,0:19:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.38,0:19:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NZoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.63,0:19:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon let's hurry up and\Nget him out of the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.34,0:19:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NI've got some medicine! Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.38,0:19:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still far too\Nearly for you to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.26,0:19:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Hawk-Eye Mihawk!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.39,0:19:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're strong but there\Nis much for you to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.43,0:20:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how many years it\Ntakes, I will hold this title as
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.56,0:20:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the greatest in the world,\Nand wait for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.32,0:20:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Until that day, you\Nmust hone your skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.49,0:20:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... seek me out!\NRoronoa Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.41,0:20:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[YOSAKU]\NPlease say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.66,0:20:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[YOSAKU, JOHNNY]\NAnything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.16,0:20:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just anyone can earn\Nthe regard of Hawk-Eye Mihawk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.08,0:20:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[MIHAWK]\NYou...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.08,0:20:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.88,0:20:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,To be the King!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.84,0:20:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Your ambitions are even\Nloftier than your friend's.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.51,0:20:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite a task.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.05,0:20:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, you just let\Nme worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.68,0:20:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Bleh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.89,0:20:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NHe's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.68,0:20:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He was just unconscious!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.31,0:20:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.39,0:20:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're alive,\Nthen say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.48,0:20:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.69,0:20:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[YOSAKU]\NBig Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.52,0:20:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NLuffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.32,0:20:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.73,0:20:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NYeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.32,0:20:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for disappointing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.11,0:20:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that you need\Nnothing less than
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.70,0:20:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the greatest swordsman\Nin the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.29,0:21:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I've let you down...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.33,0:21:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.25,0:21:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay! You can\Nstop saying things now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.50,0:21:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.80,0:21:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NI solemnly swear...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.13,0:21:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,From this moment forward...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.92,0:21:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That I will never lose again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.51,0:21:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO chokes]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.01,0:21:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the day comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.68,0:21:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...when I defeat him\Nand take his title...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.52,0:21:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I will never...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.60,0:21:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...never be defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.60,0:21:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.94,0:21:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...King of the Pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.74,0:21:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY laughs]\NYup!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.57,0:21:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a good team.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.37,0:21:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope to see you\Nagain... someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.00,0:21:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NHey! Hawk-Eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.92,0:21:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I was under the impression that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.33,0:21:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,you had come here\Nto take my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.04,0:21:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you here to kill Don\NKrieg, ruler of the East Blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.26,0:21:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The thought had\Ncrossed my mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.17,0:21:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've had enough\Nfun for today,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.88,0:21:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'm going home\Nto get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.01,0:21:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[bones cracking]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.76,0:22:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if\Nyou've had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.39,0:22:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't even gotten started.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.43,0:22:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, but, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.56,0:22:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's not a good idea\Nto try to keep him here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.40,0:22:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.98,0:22:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's time to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.07,0:22:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[MIHAWK]\NHe just won't learn, will he?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.62,0:22:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.37,0:22:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, damn... He escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.87,0:22:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.96,0:22:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS scream]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.34,0:22:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NUsopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.01,0:22:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.01,0:22:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.22,0:22:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave Nami to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.93,0:22:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NRoger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.72,0:22:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry about a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.10,0:22:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro and I are gonna\Nget her right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.02,0:22:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And make sure you get that\Ncook to join our crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.60,0:22:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.31,0:22:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...on the Going Merry,\Nthe five of us'll set sail...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.02,0:22:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...to the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.73,0:22:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY laughs]\NYeah! Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.36,0:22:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NAll right, men!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.40,0:22:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We ran into a little\Ndistraction from our plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.66,0:22:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,but the real fight starts now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.57,0:23:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna take that ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.12,0:23:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES]\NYes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.37,0:23:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHey, Pops,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.41,0:23:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,can I stop doing these chores if\NI get those pirates outta here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.83,0:23:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NSuit yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.17,0:23:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a kid, I never stopped{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.55,0:23:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Searching for a great treasure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.17,0:23:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had a map in my mind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.93,0:23:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That I knew would lead me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.06,0:23:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had to find my way{\i0}\N{\i1}to that place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.77,0:23:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before someone could beat me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.27,0:23:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promised land{\i0}\N{\i1}was in my grasp{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.90,0:23:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I wouldn't let go{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.99,0:23:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My only dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.91,0:23:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't stop chasing it{\i0}\N{\i1}until it comes true{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.54,0:23:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if the world ever changes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.84,0:23:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.68,0:24:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We could return to the time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.72,0:24:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When everything's the same{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.68,0:24:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as I'm with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.94,0:24:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My memories won't fade{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.81,0:24:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Waiting for that{\i0}\N{\i1}one true dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.66,0:24:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] Krieg and his\Npirates are on their way!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.62,0:24:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Honestly, what an\Nungrateful bunch they are...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.00,0:24:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They were given all\Nkinds of delicious food!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.79,0:24:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] Come to think of it,\Nthere's another ungrateful one
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.88,0:24:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,who took the\Ntreasure and ran off!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.38,0:24:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] Let me take care\Nof that, just get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.30,0:24:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY laughs]\NHey, that guy looks funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.09,0:24:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NHe sure has a lotta shields...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.55,0:24:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And fire! Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.97,0:24:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NOn the next One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.76,0:24:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Deadly Foot\NTechnique Bursts Forth!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.10,0:24:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji vs. The Invincible Pearl!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.56,0:24:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be\NKing of the Pirates!

